fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "gtklabel-h.html#gtk_label_get_layout_offsets", "fragment": "Gtk.Label.GetLayoutOffsets \nObtains the coordinates where the label will draw the Pango.Layout representing the text in the label useful to convert mouse events into coordinates inside the Pango.Layout e.g. to take some action if some part of the label is clicked. Remember when using the Pango.Layout functions you need to convert to and from pixels using PANGO_PIXELS not introspectable or Pango.Constants.SCALE. \nParameters \nlocation to store X offset of layout or null \nlocation to store Y offset of layout or null \n"});